			<h2 class="excerpt">略心酸</h2>
		<div class="detail">
				<p>
	Twitter
旗下的&nbsp;<span>6&nbsp;</span>秒短视频应用<span> Vine </span>三岁了。不过它庆祝生日的方式，是选择了 10个品牌曾经发过的创意视频，包括乐高、Burberry、Adidas，乐事等，先来一睹为快。<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/b18b7231bf1d.gif" width="547" height="435" title="Adidas UK" alt="Adidas UK" /><span>Adidas UK：我有独特的进球技巧</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/d049001142fb.gif" title="Burberry" alt="Burberry" /><span>Burberry</span> 
</p>
